---
// Editorial intro section - narrow centered prose on the bone page. The
// first breath after the cinematic hero. No imagery here; the type IS
// the section. Modeled on Black Tomato's "Every journey starts with a
// feeling" treatment.
---

<section class="bg-bone text-primary py-28 sm:py-40 lg:py-48">
  <div class="max-w-[720px] mx-auto px-7 lg:px-0">
    <p class="font-label-caps uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-[0.625rem] font-semibold text-primary/70 mb-10 text-center">
      The promise
    </p>
    <h2
      class="font-display font-light text-pretty leading-[1.05] tracking-[-0.025em] text-center"
      style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.5vw + 0.75rem, 3.5rem); font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 96, 'SOFT' 30, 'WONK' 0;"
    >
      Sail. Breathe.
      <span
        class="italic text-primary/85"
        style="font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 96, 'SOFT' 60, 'WONK' 1;"
      >
        Reset.
      </span>
    </h2>

    <div class="mt-12 lg:mt-16 space-y-6 font-body-lg text-[1.0625rem] lg:text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.75] text-primary/75 text-balance">
      <p>
        You don't need another vacation. You need a week where Tuesday feels
        like Saturday - where the only schedule is the tide, and the only
        notifications are dolphins off the bow.
      </p>
      <p>
        Up to twelve guests. One catamaran. A captain who reads weather
        the way other people read the news, and a host whose galley produces
        a different meal every night.
      </p>
      <p>
        We sail the British Virgin Islands, the Bahamas, and the
        Mediterranean. The boat goes where the day-charter crowds don't.
      </p>
    </div>

    <p
      class="font-serif-quote italic mt-14 lg:mt-16 text-[1.5rem] lg:text-[1.75rem] leading-[1.4] tracking-[-0.015em] text-primary text-balance text-center"
      style="font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 36, 'SOFT' 60, 'WONK' 1;"
    >
      The life you've been putting off - it starts the moment the lines come off the dock.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-14 lg:mt-16 text-center">
      <a
        href="/voyages"
        class="group inline-flex items-center gap-3 font-label-caps uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[0.75rem] font-semibold text-primary border-b-2 border-accent pb-1 hover:text-accent transition-colors"
      >
        See the Voyages
        <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" class="size-3 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M1 8h13M9 3l5 5-5 5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
